kgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709c5212b10b1ea4ff6dc65e3c3182309b43320c","tid":472871,"uid":120801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T22:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度9成人覺得拍拖係包扑野 應該唔會頂得順唔比扑嘅女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔比扑唔緊要<br />\n最煩係因為宗教原因 <br />\n一係你入佢個世界<br />\n同比佢影響埋你身邊人"},{"pid":"91dc354b9cb62606fa59563085187bdc25c44008","tid":472871,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T22:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍得拖遲早叫你返教會，你信咪無野，唔信盞搞</blockquote><br />\n最近有條仔想溝佢，佢真係帶左條仔返教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前車可鑑 <br />\n唔介意就去馬<br />\n我地都係等食花生"},{"pid":"00d6b53b4b5db0d8888622222ab3d6c4a366b081","tid":472871,"uid":120801,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"其實你地有無人諗過<br />\n佢係利用自己有幾分樣同好人格<br />\n去請一班餓男上吊入教會<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地只會對係入面<br />\n高級D的教徒有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者你係宗教 聖經 發燒友<br />\n咁佢追返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bfc4b46fdd8f721a41ace3630d3b078009be96","tid":472871,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T22:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實睇返教義 你就係魔鬼 <br />\n令佢離教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c829ede04f2ce5874576b640667fd99ce92fbf71","tid":472871,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T22:32:53.000Z","msg":"講到幾撚信耶最後咪又係比人屌到高潮反白眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0148f